00:08:25.330 --> 00:08:26.506
Saya mencari awak, dan... dan...

00:08:26.680 --> 00:08:27.376
Tidak, tidak. Saya... Saya hanya berada di...

00:08:27.550 --> 00:08:28.899
Awak... awak okay ke?

